reviewText: Wonderful family movies and arrived quickly
What can I say?  I'm a sucker for Christmas movies - even stupid ones.
Nice to watch with the grandchildren!!!
any of the three movies is worth the price - great value

I have only seen Stealing Christmas when I was younger but it is a good movie. We recently watched The Borrowers for the first time and it was great. It is more of a European or British film cast, but it was really good. It was funny and eventful. The Little People in the Floor Are REAL! Very heartwarming and sad at times. Definitely a family movie.
Great collection.
These aren't great movies, but made a nice Xmas gift.
gift for daughter she likes it
Excellent trio of family Holiday movies!
